nodes.text: Keteerians were a sentient species that inhabited the galaxy. Teroj Kee, an ally of the First Order, was a Keteerian, as was Terrib Igmusk, a hotel employee at Canto Bight.

Keteerians first appeared in the 2017 film Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi. They were first identified in the StarWars.com episode guide for "Dangerous Business," a 2019 episode of the television series Star Wars Resistance.
